          "type": "html",
          "name": "question10",
          "html": "<ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;margin-left:26px;\">\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Mediastinal dissection / opens pericardium as per trainer&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Uses retractor so as to obtain appropriate access to IMA&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Demonstrates appropriate and careful dissection of IMA as per trainer&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Demonstrates adequate blood flow in IMA&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Asks for patient to be heparinised as per local protocol&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Protects and places graft for later use as per trainer&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Ensures all branches are ligated securely&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Ensures proximal extent of harvest - adequate length to reach target&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Ensures protection of phrenic nerve&nbsp;</span></li>\n    <li><span style='line-height:115%;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-family:\"Arial\",sans-serif;font-size:9.0pt;'>Good haemostasis</span></li>\n</ol>"
         }
